[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       1640[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **School SIS integration unavailability.** IEP-aligned documentation is stored locally and queued for SIS write-back with durable retry. The SLP can export the documentation manually if needed before the retry succeeds.
